    <header>
    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 offset-md-2">
                <h2>About SingleStream</h2>
                <p>Music Is Everywhere but now you won't have to be. Music lovers shouldn't have to decide what media platform they want to use when their favorite songs are scattered across them. SingleStream puts your favorite songs from various media platforms in one place -- a combination of your favorite tracks from Napster and remixes from YouTube, together like they should be. But SingleStream isn't only a music hub -- it is a social network made of and for music enthusiasts. Share your favorite songs, explore new artists, see what your music listening history looks like and more.</p>
                </br>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    </header>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <header class="contact">
    <section id="contact" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 offset-md-2">
                <h2>Contact SingleStream</h2>
                <p>Feel free to send us an email with your questions or comments!</p>
                <ul class="list-inline banner-social-buttons">
                    <li class="list-inline-item">
                        <a href="mailto:inquiries@singlestream.online" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> <span class="network-name">E-mail Us</span></a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    </header>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p>Copyright &copy; Team 8 SingleStream 2017</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript -->
    <script src="index_resources/vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="index_resources/vendor/tether/tether.min.js"></script>
